➜正宗潮汕牛肉丸配方被公开，你吃的可能99%都不正宗！
http://www.sohu.com/a/429123295_100131509	7136
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201103/c03be479c2344a2ab59981e6d0baaf1a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>XUNCHI's TIME</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为一款"可以冷冻的潮汕味道"</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不仅安慰了在外潮汕人的胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">也让更多朋友们方便吃到正宗潮汕味</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但真材实料的潮汕牛肉丸可遇不可求</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">据说只有1%的人会辨别...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201103/8d0ef5e6ad764a42b636e6b49cf2376d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201103/a82cf0fe604a4e25a4e7b32db1c6e77f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
